name: Friend-Meleon
description:
This is a Friend-Meleon 
 
 [*] This Meleon has two faces:  
  [*] If 5 or more of your friends are playing Colormeleons the Friend-Meleon will be an angel and supports you with random paint of any common color (1 per day) 
 [*] If 4 or less of your friends are playing Colormeleons the Friend-Meleon will become a devil and hinders your meleons at dropping paint (drops will take more time, but the daily amount of drops will be the same) 
  [*] Drops if 5 or more friends are playing colormeleons at the same time 
 [*]Rarity: [color=#4B61F2]Community Meleon[/color]
 [*]Made by:[color=#4B61F2]Magic Genie[/color]

name: ColorMeLion
description:
A ColorMeLion is the strongest meleon ingame! It will use its strenght to tidy up your studio - or to steal your empty cans of paint, so you can't refill them! 
 
 [*] Dropped for all players who got the Random Meleon by accident and can be found in Studio 
   [*] If the ColorMeLion brings a can of paint out of the studio you can't reuse this color ingame! 
   [*]Rarity: [color=#4B61F2]CustoMeleon[/color]

name: Skeleton-Meleon
description:
This Meleon brings fear and terror to your Studio! There is really no good reason to own it! [color=#ffd700]Don't buy it![/color] If it drops into your inventory, try to trade it to somebody who don't understand why you will give it away   
  
 [*] Makes your meleons run away in fear - they will not drop any paint while a Skeleton-Meleon is nearby 
  [*] They destroy your artwork 
  [*] They will steal your paint (non permanent) 
 [*]rarity: [color=#ffd700]Event Meleon[/color]
 [*] This great meleon was made by [color=#4B61F2][url=http://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198119982900]DimkaKMS[/url][/color]!

 [*] This box will NOT contain any collectables which dropped for everyone for a limited time (like Beta-Items) and NO Supportmeleons 
  [*] More Yojka Boxes can be found in boxes! 
  [*] You can unbox this box ingame by clicking on it! (But not before Yojkas birthday!)

name: Christmasbox 2020
description:
A christmas gift from your Dev 
  [*] Can be opened only with the right code 
 
 [*] Will be destroyed with the wrong code 
  [*] To open it: enter the right code in the field, then try to open the box 
  [*]rarity: [color=#ffd700] just for 24 hours[/color] 
 
 [*] Thank you for the idea,[color=#4B61F2] fqpl[/color]!
